lead_paragraph: Fernando Alonso would be on the list of possible replacements for retired Formula One world champion Nico Rosberg at Mercedes despite his contract with McLaren, according to team boss Toto Wolff.

headline.print_headline: Mercedes Have to Consider Alonso, Says Wolff
headline.main: Mercedes Have to Consider Alonso, Says Wolff
